="" width="628" height="221" /></a><br />\n从代码编辑器的左上角，我们可以看到应用名为wp4sae，代码版本为2。然后我们点击&#8221;Config&#8221;打开对应应用版本的AppConfig进行编辑：<br />\n<a href="http://wp4sae-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2011/09/appconfig_3.png" rel="lightbox[120]"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-130" title="appconfig_3" src="http://wp4sae-wordpress.stor.sinaapp.com/uploads/2011/09/appconfig_3.png" alt="" width="1280" height="284" /></a><br />\n在文本框中按照自己需要修改完AppConfig配置后，点击上面的&#8221;Save&#8221;保存就可以了。<br />\n保存成功后，在&#8221;Save&#8221;右边的状态栏中就会显示一个红底白字的&#8221;saved&#8221;。<br />\n如果格式错误，会弹出错误提示框，将格式修改正确后再保存即可。<br />\nAppConfig配置格式等请参考 <a href="http://sae.sina.com.cn/?m=devcenter&amp;catId=193" target="_blank">SAE官方文档</a></p>\n<div style=float:left><!-- JiaThis Button BEGIN -->\r\n<div id="jiathis_style_32x32">\r\n	<a class="jiathis_button_tsina"></a>\r\n	<a class="jiathis_button_twitter"></a>\r\n	<a class="jiathis_button_tqq"></a>\r\n	<a class="jiathis_button_qzone"></a>\r\n	<a class="jiathis_button_renren"></a>\r\n	<a class="jiathis_button_kaixin001"></a>\r\n	<a href="http://www.jiathis.com/share/" class="jiathis jiathis_txt jtico jtico_jiathis" target="_blank"></a>\r\n	<a class="jiathis_counter_style"></a>\r\n</div>\r\n<script type="text/javascript" src="http://v2.jiathis.com/code/jia.js" charset="utf-8"></script>\r\n<!-- JiaThis Button END -->|2|left</div><table class="wumii-related-items" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3" border="0"  style="clear: both;">\r\n    \r\n    <tr>\r\n        <td colspan="4"><b><font size="-1"  style="display: block !important; padding: 20px 0 5px !important;">您可能也喜欢：</font></b></td>\r\n    </tr>\r\n    \r\n        <tr>\r\n                <td width="102" valign="top" style="padding: 5px !important; margin: 0 !important;">\r\n                    <a target="_blank" title="WordPress 3.2.1 for SAE 已上线到SAE应用商店" style="text-decoration: none !important; cursor: pointer !important;" href="http://app.wumii.com/ext/redirect?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwp4sae.org%2F2011%2F08%2Fwo